User
    - Id (PK)
    - Name
    - Email
    - Password
    - Contact

Role
    - Id (PK)
    - Name
    - Description
    - CreatedAt

Permission (Optional)
    - Id (PK)
    - Name
    - Description

    User-Role
        - UserId (FK)
        - RoleId (FK)

    Goal
        - Id (PK)
        - CreatedBy (FK -> UserID)
        - Name
        - Description
        - StartDate
        - EndDate
        - Status
        - Priority
        - CreatedAt
        - UpdatedAt
        - Version
    
    Goal_Log (Notification Service will query this)
        - Id (PK)
        - GoalID (FK)
        - ApprovedBy (FK -> UserID)
        - ApprovedAt 

        Budget
            - Id (PK)
            - CreatedBy (FK -> UserID)
            - GoalId (FK)
            - Name
            - Description
            - Amount
            - StartDate
            - EndDate
            - Status
            - ApprovalCount
            - CreatedAt
            - UpdatedAt
            - Version

        Budget_Log (Notification Service will query this)
            - Id (PK)
            - BudgetId (FK)
            - ApprovedBy (FK -> UserID)
            - ApprovedAt

Reminder

Notification


